* this chapter deals with Text Processing using filters like
	
	sed, awk, wc, grep, etc,.
	

* the folder contain 

	* ".awk" files => these are stand-alone awk scripts
		=> they are used for organizing text in a file
			or output of a command like "who"
			
	* ex5_1, ex5_2 => chapter excercises

	* course_proj_4 => course project PHASE IV

	* names.dat => a data file for storing records
		used by course_proj_* scripts

	* ".png" file => screenshot of a script running
